TopicTitle: game crash when flying a random experimental vessel

Articles.Content:
i made a small testing vessel to test ksp warp drive 

 however after many attempts ksp crashes at some point , after i load back where the vessel was located at (runway) the ksp crashes and an unity  window opens up and later on everything closes:
